task.summary: Default task

Fixed some balancing issues with high traffic and added many other stuff.
Added hot-code reload, which basically reloads all workers when php code has changed. Added debug option. Added logging option. Increase performance and removed Stackable stuff. Added config command to configure ppm.json. Added static file server. Fixed Symfony bootstrap so the profiler works more correctly (but not yet perfect)
updated deps
Removed checkSlaves since its not in practical use. Adjusted readme a bit to new config options
Echo the correct host

Redirect stdout/stderr from slave to masters outputs.
Fixed also initial hot-code checking
Fixed parsing of content-type, case mismatch
added files support to httpKernel
Made cookies working, correct content-type parsing of request, correct header sending for response.
Correct $_SERVER header name
Added concurrent-requests option for application that support it.
Added note concurrent-requests and workers.

Started with better debugging experience when having exceptions in the actual application.
Also improved process communication handling.

Better debugging experience when having exceptions in the actual application, especially in the bootstrap.
Also improved process communication handling. Added emergency mode when application bootsrap failed. Added better stderr printing from workers. Added auto file scanning each 0.5 sec for hot-code reload.
